{"tid":2500184,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"[牛扒師] 自家製 32日乾式熟成 澳洲黑安格斯牛小排","createTime":"2021-04-22T12:20:18.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-22T14:42:40.000Z","uid":260581,"like":14,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"b2ec19f7650392d97a4cda0e8aa8eb5894c54b4a","tid":2500184,"uid":260581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-22T12:20:18.000Z","msg":"大家好<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我一個月前買左呢舊牛小排<br />\nDry aged完諗住黎打邊爐<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢舊野唔係和牛，係純黑安格斯牛<br />\n但係佢個油花達到和牛既m5<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmXWqiBiusnBpUUGAjX9JkukJxCCmUCCkwRDpnyjWW3RyY?filename=1mDWMK3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1mDWMK3.jpg&h=7499aa46&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmZpkLk3WkhNmijfXERjX1QnLDi5o4wMXHPPmXPatfa7jF?filename=LhghwbK.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLhghwbK.jpg&h=ce28c0b5&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/Qma5V6eExS6H1hWQZdMRv7V7gGdPQCSFtRMeMxnnKQ1Rty?filename=bF34bbL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbF34bbL.jpg&h=07d4c78d&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmP1wStyZ8ax5nsnTiY5iGp7tUYs652G956oa9nok3Qr17?filename=Yvdr8Yr.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYvdr8Yr.jpg&h=00483c15&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n32日後<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/cigar.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmdQMAWwXYhmY5fpDirVASKMfVa47aH3quDbjLS3Huz6Zr?filename=WuRdOZz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWuRdOZz.jpg&h=35b321a6&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmX8DdeL3T3guRHb28LoaHytH7B8EBrBxEqbXxuXWXdz6w?filename=QvVKbcV.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQvVKbcV.jpg&h=f031cf40&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmV8QyGVtLsjSFgsbxsudXEKWMoVsWkCLyaDyQ1pDRMj1r?filename=pjaaRcV.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpjaaRcV.jpg&h=e296c32f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n切後<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/power.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/power.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/power.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/Qmcmqtn48jJr6juJ1Tj68woYuCfEJgFZBZ6jcDFx1XxwFi?filename=4Q0FtZP.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4Q0FtZP.jpg&h=54f469e7&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmSCqCyPArc4L2t5hRAN3QKv5nnwg7Er3mmddrPU9hbaaH?filename=eLk96Mu.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FeLk96Mu.jpg&h=de904988&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmZoE1ogomPaA3VbegikRdJbJWYmXicx7rU64cDtS8Zdix?filename=fOuKVEQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfOuKVEQ.jpg&h=4b5f1f89&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmVuSneJJsrxQFBG9JFyaVRbYYM3vWGdgoxesoGuL6kdE1?filename=L737Trw.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FL737Trw.jpg&h=ee21d6f0&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmWCDnVs3ADLD6z8aq5PhUEp56SfsmqKT6yRmPtwisGvb9?filename=Yc7c4yc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYc7c4yc.jpg&h=a521e9b3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n舊肉切完第一刀真心當場射到腳軟<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n因為舊肉細，所以我原本都諗住28日，唔好太耐，多左幾日係ok的<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不過唔知舊肉係咪有骨，所以32日都好香<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nTrim曬之後，連埋off cuts得返1kg肉<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好想快d拎去打邊爐<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bacc00081a3d446458bb5099b8561d99f4b92532","tid":2500184,"uid":199380,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-22T12:21:11.000Z","msg":"幾時煮嚟食<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/crowd.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/crowd.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/crowd.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cf0f5fd61f2dff0f8462c02fba5954246da517a2","tid":2500184,"uid":390941,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-22T12:21:55.000Z","msg":"其實係咪要每切一下就抹一下刀？"},{"pid":"d6919e7a482cf29daf77e4af471e8e77548cca66","tid":2500184,"uid":281492,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-22T12:30:06.000Z","msg":"正呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0c5dd6d67d244cb235c1e9c99b0f5cbdd9abc842","tid":2500184,"uid":313